@node MAIN
@title "The Gamma Invasion"
==============================================================================
                            The Gamma Invasion
==============================================================================
         A scenario for the game "-Star_Trek-" by Frank Mathieson
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

+++ UNITED FEDERATION OF PLANETS
+++ STARFLEET HEADQUARTERS
+++ STARDATE 53226.1
+++ ADMIRAL X.CRAMER

Dear Captain H. SCHNEIDER,

the Dominion has sent out a fleet of improved Jem'Hadar warships of a
new, unknown class in order to take over the Alpha Quadrant. Our recons
report, that they have much more fire power and much stronger shield
systems now, so the situation is serious.

The galaxy class USS ROYAL (NCC-1801) has order to defeat the Jem'Hadar
at any cost.

Good luck, Captain!
==============================================================================
