@node SCENARIOOVERVIEW
@title "What is in this scenario?"

@{b}OVERVIEW@{ub}

Estimated difficulty: Hard
Solvable with unregistered version: Maybe (not tested)

Another hard one: The Jem'Hadar are really strong this time and only
a few of your Federation allies can become strong enough to defeat
them. So upgrade your ship and do the best you can...
_____________________________________________________________________

ENEMY UNITS

24x Dominion Warship (NEW JEM'HADAR CLASS)     490
 6x Cardassian Cruiser (GALOR CLASS)           300
_____________________________________________________________________

YOUR UNITS

 7x Starbase
USS CAIRO (NCC-42136, EXCELSIOR CLASS)         400
USS GORKON (NCC-50446, EXCELSIOR CLASS)        350
USS ENTERPRISE (NCC-1701-E, SOVEREIGN CLASS)   425
USS DEFIANT (NX-74205, DEFIANT CLASS)          450
USS BOZEMAN (NCC-1941, SOYUZ CLASS)            280
